Class ToFloatNoScaling

  • Object
    • VoxelsConverter<FloatBuffer>
      • ToFloatNoScaling

  • public final class ToFloatNoScaling
extends VoxelsConverter<FloatBuffer>
    Converts voxel buffers to a FloatBuffer without scaling any values.
